ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Sure! It was nice to learn a bit of history and do a technological survey of robotics.
Yes I would recommend it. You do learn a lot about robotics and the final project allows you to conduct a real robotics experiment, which is very interesting.
